<paragraph pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Topotypes: BRAZIL: Amazonas: from Sattler collection 23, Sattler, 2 larvae, 2 male metamorphotypes, 4 adult metamorphotypes of undetermined gender (NMNH).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Presumably named for the country of Brazil, where the species was collected.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
